claim.claim-text:
1. A semiconductor laser comprising:
a p-type InP substrate containing zinc;
an undoped InP layer on said substrate and electrically connected to said substrate and having a carrier concentration of 3×1017 cm−3 or less;
a p-type InP cladding layer on said undoped InP layer;
an active layer on said p-type InP cladding layer and generating a laser beam;
an n-type InP cladding layer on said active layer and containing n-type dopants; and
an n-type contact layer on said n-type InP cladding layer and electrically connected to said n-type InP cladding layer.
